        <p>
            Use the formulas for <m>s(t)</m> and <m>v(t)</m> you got in <xref ref="analytic_solution"/> and the single pitch data in <xref ref="pitch_data"/> and try to solve for <m>k</m> algebraically. Say where you get stuck. (Be careful with your units.)
        </p>
